title: Best-Ever Chicken Enchilada Soup
ingredients: ['1 tablespoon vegetable oil', '450g boneless, skinless chicken breast fillets', '80g onion, diced', '1 clove garlic, finely chopped', '1 litre chicken stock', '115g masa harina', '750ml water, divided', '250g enchilada sauce', '450g Kraft processed cheese slices, unwrapped and chopped', '1 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon chilli powder', '1/2 teaspoon ground cumin']
